params._featureIndices: The feature indices to append to the array held by this contract.

params._classifications: The classifications supported by the model.
params._intercept: The bias to add to the multiplication of the weights and the data. Multiplied by `toFloat`.
params._learningRate: (Optional, defaults to 1). The amount of impact that new training data has to the weights. Multiplied by `toFloat`.
params._weights: The weights for the model. Each multiplied by `toFloat`.
